text: <../images/lbar.gif>huæd gebyreð ðe and me to wircanne wundar ær min fæder uælle of heofnum gelefa.
<../images/lbar.gif>eghuælc an uæs tui sestre gemet uel<../images/lbar.gif>ðrea fullunga.
Heofuncund mettihuitcorn sonuuald for huætte cuom of heofnum and feoll on Moisi mið his folce on ðam more ðer he uæs.
Ðes latzar micel gebecnas in deiglo gehryno.
<../images/lbar.gif>þæt unberende treo he genimes, unberende uæstem.
Ðreat turma.i. XXXII  equitestuu and ðrittih eorodmonna.
Þæt uitgadom and allra canone cuido ðaðe ymb cristes ðroung acueden uæs<../images/lbar.gif>weron.
Ðus Beda ðe broema boecere cuæð.
On ðæm dæge gearuadon hiora mett to eastrosymble.
